name: User is able to see the fuel types and car wash service on store widget
description: User is able to see the fuel types and car wash icons
descriptionHtml: User is able to see the fuel types and car wash icons

testStage.description: User is able to see the fuel types and car wash icons

steps.name: I set the location of the device to "DENMARK_10150"
I mock the location of the device to "DENMARK_10150"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "DENMARK_10150" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "DENMARK_10150" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I swipe on the device screen to the to refresh Home Page
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Station Widget" is displayed
I check that the "FUEL 92 Icon" is displayed
I check that the "FUEL 95 Icon" is displayed
I check that the "DIESEL Icon" is displayed
I check that the "CARWASH Icon" is displayed
